        public static java.lang.String getLicensePath(java.lang.String s_uri)
        Gets a path of the file that license exist. There are 3 possible files on GitHub: LICENSE, COPYING, README. This path is basic an online link to that file. You MUST give the directory of the project as a parameter to be able to do this.

      • loadPrimitiveData

        public static void loadPrimitiveData()
                              throws java.io.IOException
        Load Primitive Data into the crawler. With that function you can load any data written on your own or collected before with the crawler (a previous state). The default file is being called primitiveness.lcdata and is been loaded from the default directory of the program. Note that at the beginning the default projects list of the crawler is being deleted.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
